						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">Disch wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">Is surface blitting even still supported by modern hardware?</div>
<br />Nvidia cards only do point sampling on Vista+.  I switched to Direct3D because of this.
<br />
<br />I'm using the method described <a href="http://www.iquilezles.org/www/articles/texture/texture.htm" class="postlink">here</a> for resizing.  It results in a smooth image, but edge detail is better preserved than with straight bilinear filtering.</div>

